<headline>Special Weather Statement issued March 08 at 12:55AM MST  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Light Snow through the Morning...
Light snow will continue across Fergus and Chouteau Counties
through the morning hours, with additional snowfall accumulations
of up to 1 inch being possible across most lower elevations. Some
north facing mid-slope locations in the island ranges could see
an additional 3 inches of snow. Travelers should be prepared for
slippery roadways, especially bridges and overpasses. Slow down
and allow extra time to travel.</description>
